					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Two gith kids are pushing a chest (which secretly contains a gremishka) back and forth between them using their Mage Hands. You can tell them to stop and if you insist, eventually they'll step back from the box, letting the gremishka break out. Alternatively, if you try to join in or fail to get them to stop, they'll start shoving you. "
				}
